{"id":81604,"title":"Frequently asked questions in direct pulp capping of permanent teeth.","abstract":"Direct pulp capping is a proven method of preserving tooth vitality of a mature permanent tooth in cases of pulp exposures. The indications for this treatment, treatment modalities and materials are discussed in this paper.This paper answers many of the frequently asked questions by general practitioners, dental students and specialists about direct pulp capping.","date":"2014-06-16","categories":"Stomatognathic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24930251","annotations":[{"name":"General practitioner","weight":0.135327,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/General_practitioner"},{"name":"Tooth","weight":0.116383,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tooth"},{"name":"Permanent teeth","weight":0.0290048,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Permanent_teeth"},{"name":"Paper","weight":0.0227187,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paper"},{"name":"Musical mode","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Musical_mode"},{"name":"General officer","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/General_officer"},{"name":"Exposure (photography)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Exposure_(photography)"},{"name":"Vitality","weight":0.0162839,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vitality"},{"name":"FAQ","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/FAQ"},{"name":"Pulp (tooth)","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pulp_(tooth)"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Dentistry","weight":0.0136738,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dentistry"}]}
